I listened him carefully and I am certain that PS5 is going to be a unique device much better than Xbox series X. Though Xbox series X is having edge in teraflops but this difference in teraflops between the two consoles is not going to make a big difference in graphics nor in console's success. Why am I saying this? Because it is not the console that wins, it's games which make a console attain high sales. Sony has better exclusives undoubtedly. Moreover PS5 appears to be made a more smarter device with better Harmony between it's components. Finally what people missing is their audio work. Imagine watching a horror movie without audio will not feel horrible because acoustic has a huge impact on perception and feelings and brain responce. Sony is really smart because this audio leap will be huge for people experiencing PS5. I think Sony PS5 is going to be a blockbuster.
Thanks
Games lover
